FLW FTW! If you have any interest in Frank Lloyd Wright, it's pretty much a no-brainer to take a trip to Taliesin West if you're in the area. I took the 90-minute tour and had an excellent guide, Dierdre, whose knowledge of FLW's life and works, as well as the minutiae of Taliesen West, made it a very informative visit. Well worth the $30+ price of admission.

